# MetaWave Innovations Visual Style & Theme Guide (MWITHEME)

This document outlines the official design system, typography, color palette, gradients, and interactive tokens used across the **MetaWave Innovations** digital ecosystem.

---

## 1. Design & Aesthetic Philosophy
MetaWave Innovations utilizes a **Swiss-Modern, Premium Corporate Minimalist** aesthetic. 
* **Mood:** Trustworthy, highly technical, clean, and forward-looking.
* **Layout:** Generous negative space, rounded corners (`rounded-2xl` and `rounded-3xl`), precise borders (`border-slate-200/90`), and subtle radial glowing highlights to denote active server nodes and modern web frameworks.

---

## 2. Typography Strategy

Our visual identity relies on three high-quality typeface pairings, imported directly via Google Fonts:

| Font Classification | Family | Primary Use Case |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Primary Sans-Serif** | `Inter` | Body copy, secondary descriptions, paragraphs, form labels, and UI state elements. |
| **High-Impact Display** | `Plus Jakarta Sans` | Hero headers, titles, section headings, and cards. Designed for structural layout elegance. |
| **Monospace Accent** | `JetBrains Mono` | Code blocks, compilation status markers, numeric statistics, system telemetry tags, and metadata stamps. |

---

## 3. Core Color Palette

### A. Brand Core Colors
* **MetaWave Primary Green (`#326E45`):** Represents growth, sustainable systems engineering, and elite performance. Used for primary interactive triggers, hover states, and brand highlights.
* **Sovereign Dark Slate (`#0A0F1C`):** Used for solid headers, custom dark campaign cards, deep overlays, and code consoles.
* **Sovereign Dark Blue-Navy (`#0E1527`):** Immersive visual campaign backdrop container shading.
* **Premium Background Canvas (`#FAFBFD`):** High-contrast, clean off-white canvas which reduces eye fatigue while keeping UI elements extremely distinct.
* **Primary Slate Body Text (`#1E293B`):** Warm, high-readability gray/black used for optimal reader comfort.

