## 5. Layout & Element Styling Standards

* **Borders:** Subtle slate borders (`border border-slate-200/90`) that change to soft emerald hues on hover (`hover:border-emerald-500/30`).
* **Shadows:** Standard light shadow (`shadow-sm`) transitioning on interaction to a rich, double-layered premium shadow:
  * `hover:shadow-[0_25px_50px_-12px_rgba(16,185,129,0.12),0_8px_24px_-4px_rgba(15,23,42,0.04)]`
* **Elevations & Scales:** Staggered spring transforms:
  * `hover:scale-[1.02] hover:-translate-y-1.5 transition-all duration-300`
